Gets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionDuration"></xref> that represents a permanent redirection.
A permanent redirection duration indicates the new location(s) specified should be used permanently for the given scope.

Gets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionDuration"></xref> that represents a temporary redirection.
A temporary redirection duration indicates the new location(s) that are valid for a limited time frame for the given scope.
This is the default value for <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionDuration>.
